{"tid":1741074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【招人】香港毒氣APPS籌備中！","createTime":"2019-11-20T07:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T08:46:37.000Z","uid":341080,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1a78f8a5c644951064c3e2b4e1b9f9b2b808cf30","tid":1741074,"uid":341080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:31:41.000Z","msg":"各位師兄好，我第一次玩連登，請多多指教！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人廢青一名，上星期學校停課冇工開，所以就整理咗催淚彈發射資料，前幾日請槍放上連登，至今已經有<span style=\"color: orange;\">十三萬</span>點擊率。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊post: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1729176\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1729176</a><br />\n附地圖：<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=1J0xABJYyqeY7V9BBAd-Q_ZCY3Mn22wok&amp;ll=22.382581894986814%2C114.10570435&amp;z=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F0%2Fembed%3Fmid%3D1J0xABJYyqeY7V9BBAd-Q_ZCY3Mn22wok%26ll%3D22.382581894986814%252C114.10570435%26z%3D11&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=6e646b1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=1J0xABJYyqeY7V9BBAd-Q_ZCY3Mn22wok&amp;ll=22.382581894986814%2C114.10570435&amp;z=11</a><br />\n<br />\n入正題先，因為資料一路加，google map不勝負荷，會越來越慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以同另一位催淚彈地圖製作人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">商討會把所有data整成apps!</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另外會加上<span style=\"color: pink;\">風向對區域影響</span>，<span style=\"color: pink;\">二噁英指數</span>，<span style=\"color: pink;\">集合有關催淚彈禍害的文宣</span> (<ins>大家有咩意見可以補充</ins>)。<br />\n<br />\n暫時團隊中有化學家，地理學家....但我地仲需要各位大大幫手！￼所以，現在希望招人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">-文宣隊！非常重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-寫apps隊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-各方面的專家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位有興趣人士都可以pm tg @woohooha </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩大家幫我大大力推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />十萬火急，趕住要人！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d69f0186b853bd2eda68d70872b1539d305545","tid":1741074,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:34:06.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"1ac18eea6d918504d955dadb61a9582f9c30ef96","tid":1741074,"uid":153268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"人黎啊！！人黎啊！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a0c44437b6c16ae484db1e665c1694f73da73b","tid":1741074,"uid":153268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:34:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40d156e7ef305b04d6ae8755e73e5a39e1080b25","tid":1741074,"uid":153268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"一推再推"},{"pid":"f773033240c7740b6a750f316cf50e90d5c7e3ad","tid":1741074,"uid":153268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse